introduction.p:
Let us examine the crest of the waves at t=0.  The crests will occur when the argument of the cosine is equal to 2n\pi for n an integer.

	-kx + \phi = 2 n \pi\ \ \Longrightarrow\ \ x = \text{constant}

Thus, a plane wave moving along x axis crests simultaneously at all points of planes parallel to the yz plane separated by one wavelength.
